XYOFF - X-Y source position offset

Syntax:   XYOFF=<xoff>,<yoff>
Response: XYOFF/<xoff>,<yoff>

Settable parameters:
<x>: offset in X coordinate, in numeric angle/degrees format.
     Response is in degrees.
<y>: offset in Y coordinate, in numeric angle/degrees format.
     Response is in degrees.

Monitor-only parameters: none

      Comments: The antenna will move to the offset position when
this command is issued. To return to the on-source position, issue
